						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone in the compound of the Hanumān temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records the death by <hi rend="italic">samādhi</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Boppa-gauḍa</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Mākanūr,</hi> the disciple of <hi rend="bold">Nandi-Bhaṭṭāraka</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Mūlasaṁgha</hi> and <hi rend="bold">Sūrastha-gaṇa.</hi> The inscription is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Khara, Kārtika s11u. Friday.</hi> The characters belong to about the <hi rend="bold">12-13th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
